RELIVE THE 2024 GLOBAL MEETING


Over two unforgettable days, our global community gathered for our 19th annual Global Meeting, and what a special event it was.

We shared stories, ideas, and dreams of a world where unity and gender equality go hand in hand, and came together with open hearts and a shared commitment to driving real change.

Together, we felt the power of connection, the strength of shared purpose, and the beauty of collective action.
